query:
SELECT p.id as planId, p.name as planName, t.id as toolId, t.name as toolName 
FROM planTools pt 
JOIN plans p ON pt.planId = p.id 
JOIN tools t ON pt.toolId = t.id 
WHERE p.id = 1;
